ChangeList.Description: Added the [deletePasswordSingleSignOnCredentials](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/user?view=graph-rest-beta) method to the [user](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/user?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the [getPasswordSingleSignOnCredentials](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/user?view=graph-rest-beta) method to the [user](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/user?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added two new methods to the [user](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/user?view=graph-rest-beta) resource for managing Password SSO credentials
